                    <span class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">Epiroc</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 flex items-center justify-center h-20">
                    <span class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">Wirtgen</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange-500 mb-4">Africa</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        Extensive network across African mining regions, supplying premium equipment and supporting local mining operations with authorized parts and service.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange-500 mb-4">Europe</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        Strategic partnerships with European equipment manufacturers and technology providers for cutting-edge mining solutions and technical support.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section id="faq" class="py-20 bg-white">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-8 lg:px-16">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">{{faq.title}}</h2>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                    {{faq.description}}
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6">
                <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
                    <button class="w-full text-left flex justify-between items-center" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">What types of mining equipment do you supply?</h3>
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="mt-4 text-gray-600 hidden">
                        <p>We supply a comprehensive range of mining equipment including excavators, bulldozers, drilling rigs, crushers, conveyor systems, and specialized processing machinery. Our equipment is suitable for open-pit mining, underground operations, and various mineral processing applications.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
                    <button class="w-full text-left flex justify-between items-center" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Do you provide equipment maintenance and support?</h3>
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="mt-4 text-gray-600 hidden">
                        <p>Yes, we provide comprehensive maintenance and technical support services. Our team of certified technicians offers regular maintenance, emergency repairs, spare parts supply, and training programs to ensure optimal equipment performance and longevity.</p>
