                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="mt-4 text-gray-600 hidden">
                        <p>We adhere to the highest international safety standards including ISO 45001 for occupational health and safety management. Our comprehensive safety protocols ensure the wellbeing of all personnel and compliance with local and international regulations.</p>
                    </div>
